java.lang.Object

eu.europa.esig.dss.xades.validation.XAdESBaselineRequirementsChecker
public class XAdESBaselineRequirementsChecker extends BaselineRequirementsChecker<XAdESSignature>
Performs checks according to EN 319 132-1 v1.1.1 "6.3 Requirements on XAdES signature's elements, qualifying properties and services"
